when we create curly braces it creates a scope. CURLY BRACKETS DEFINE A BLOCK OF SCOPE , ANYTHING DECLARED BETWEEN CURLY BRACKS
GOES OUT OF SCOPE AFTER THE CLOSING BRACKET.

